&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino;&quot;&gt;Evaluate and manage vascular conditions such as venous insufficiency, pelvic congestion syndrome, and peripheral arterial disease.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
