&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As a Clinical Technologist, you’ll be a critical member of our team, supporting patient flow and engaging in various clinical support tasks. After completing your initial training (4-6 weeks), you’ll perform all job responsibilities independently with confidence. This entry-level role is ideal for MAs and PCTs looking to expand their skills and take on new challenges in a fast-paced clinic environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
